Class MDDImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MDD, SF, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class MDDImpl
extends SFImpl
implements MDD
    An implementation of the model object 'MDD'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Xm Base
    • Ym Base
    • Xm Units
    • Ym Units
    • Xm Size
    • Ym Size
    • MDD Flgs
    • Triplets
